metadata.description:
The "Sinematic" NFT is a 5 song album and the debut collection by NFT Jingles. It is an ERC-1155 token on the Ethereum blockchain. We've made it so you can play the music right here from your wallet! That same music is also available to stream for free, but owning the NFT comes with exclusive perks. Sinematic being in your wallet means you are one step closer to obtaining true financial freedom... All you have to do is listen to the music. Welcome to the new age of entertainment.

Tracks:

Track 1 - Hato(Feat. Cloudy The Weatherman & Rooks)

Track 2 - Love & Sin(Feat. Dieverse24k & Cloudy The Weatherman)

Track 3 - Prototype(Feat. Tek47 & Cloudy The Weatherman)

Track 4 - What's The Operation(Feat. Cloudy The Weatherman & Lucky)

Track 5 - Sinematic(Feat. Cloudy The Weatherman) (edited)
